================================================================================
PART 4: Universal diagonal gauge transformation
================================================================================

If B_k = D_k * B_0 * E_k for diagonal D_k, E_k, then:
  rank(B_k) = rank(B_0) automatically (diagonal matrices are invertible)
  This would PROVE eigenspace Betti uniformity!

